

**Mo g Paul ab i ha tahni g hoꞌigeꞌidahuna **

1 Ab g wo e hoꞌigeꞌidahun, t-wepnag, k ab wo tai g Jiosh mat pi ab hu wo e shohbi g haꞌichu t-ahga ab amjed t-kownalig Jesus. T muꞌijj ab wo si has i elid k ab wo s-wohog el hab masma mo am hab e wua em-shahgid. 2 Pi ap hehemajkam o pi ab hu wohochud g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga ch ab t-wui gegok. Kumt am wo si e hoꞌigeꞌidahunad mat wo t-doꞌibia g Jiosh ab ha amjed. 

3 Jiosh at hemho wa am hab wo juh mo haschu i t-ahgid. S-mahch ach mat ab wo i em-mah g gewkdag k wo em-nuhkud mat pi wo em-gehg g Jiawul. 4 Dam t-wehm wohochuddam. Kuch heg hekaj hab em-elid mam am hab junihim hegai mach ab i em-mashcham ch am hab wabsh wo i junihid. 5 Ch ab i tahni g t-kownalig Jesus mat hab wo em-juh mamt baꞌich wo i mai g Jiosh pihk elidadag k wo s-chu nakogad hab masma mo hab masma g Jesus Christ. 

**Mattsh wo chum s-wapagimak **

6 Heki ach hu em-mashcham mamt wo s-wapagimak. K eda haꞌi hegam mo d wohochuddam s-papadma ch pi am hu oidch hab e junihim g t-mashchama. Ch ab em-chehani g t-kownalig Jesus Christ gewkdagkaj mamt pi am hu wo ha wehmajk. 7 Am am wa t-neid mach wa pi shaꞌi papadma mach wa am em-wehmajkahim. Kum am wa s-mahch mamt am chum t-oidk hab wo wa masmak. 8 Si ach wa chikpan chum hems s-chuhugam k ed matt am wo wa haꞌichu ha namkidad hegam mach hedai i kih am dadha mamt pi haꞌichu wo heki gei t-wehhejed. 

9 Bo hi wa chum mahs mach apꞌedag mamt ab haꞌichu wo i t-namkid nach pi d Jiosh pionag em-wehhejed. Ch wa wabshaba hejel t-dagioꞌid matt am wo em-chehgi mamt has wo chum masmak. 10 Bach wa em-ahgid mach eda am em-wehmaj mamt pi wo ha gegos hegam mo pi tatchua mat wo chikpanad. 11 Kah ach mo am em-shahgid haꞌi s-papadma ch pi chikpan ch wabsh himchud g has ahgadag. 12 Ch ab si ha chehani g t-kownalig Jesus Christ gewkdagkaj ch ab ha gewkemhun mat am wabsh wo i e bahbgi k wo chikpanad ch hekaj wo e dagioꞌidad. 

13 Kumt ahpim mam wabsh s-ap am hab e junihim am hab wabsh wo i junihid g s-apꞌekam ch pi wo dagito 14 ch wabshaba wabsh wo dagito hegai matp hedai pi ab hu wo wohog elidad ihda mani ia em-chehani. Tp hems ab wo wa bei g si edadag k am wo i e apꞌech. 15 Am g wo s-chegitok mo pi d em-obga ch wabshaba d em-wepnag mamt ab wo shohbidad haꞌichukaj. 

**Mat ia i kuhgi g e-oꞌohana g Paul **

16 Chum at hekid am wo em-wehmajk g t-kownalig Jesus. Kuch ab tahni mat chum hekid baꞌich ab wo i em-mahkad g s-ap tahhadkam. 

17 Ahni Paul ant ia hahawa si hejel haꞌichu wo oꞌoha hab masma mani hab wa wua an wehs ni-oꞌohana ed. Mt hab masma wo s-mahchk mani d ahni. 

18 Neh, ab at wo baꞌich i s-em-hoꞌigeꞌel g t-kownalig Jesus Christ.


